<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730210344644015801.jpg" title="1730210344644015801.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215211.jpg" width="877" height="670" style="width: 877px; height: 670px;"/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10月23日上午，江西省2025届民办本科高校毕业生综合招聘会暨江西软件职业技术大学秋季双选会在我校田径场盛大召开，现场人潮涌动，盛况空前。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730210462622074319.jpg" title="1730210462622074319.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215253.jpg" width="882" height="558" style="width: 882px; height: 558px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 双选会由校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭主持，会议共分五项议程：</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 01.校党委书记、督导专员饶勇致辞</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 02.江西尚首信息技术有限公司董事长徐明致辞</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 03.南昌市湾里管理局党工委副书记涂晔致辞</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 04.江西省教育评估监测研究院党委委员、副院长唐旭致辞</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 05.与会领导共同启动招聘会</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730210516724053337.jpg" title="1730210516724053337.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215225.jpg" width="891" height="633" style="width: 891px; height: 633px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">▲校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">主持会议</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730210578450030063.jpg" title="1730210578450030063.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215247.jpg" width="892" height="661" style="width: 892px; height: 661px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">▲校党委书记、督导专员饶勇致辞</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730210711852060891.jpg" title="1730210711852060891.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029220614.jpg" width="898" height="554" style="width: 898px; height: 554px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">▲江西尚首信息技术有限公司董事长</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">徐明致辞</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730210812995000778.jpg" title="1730210812995000778.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215157.jpg" width="906" height="615" style="width: 906px; height: 615px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">▲南昌市湾里管理局党工委副书记</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">涂晔致辞</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730210873473063209.jpg" title="1730210873473063209.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215219.jpg" width="906" height="616" style="width: 906px; height: 616px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">▲江西省教育评估监测研究院党委委员、</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">副院长唐旭致辞</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730210926349006241.jpg" title="1730210926349006241.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215231.jpg" width="911" height="575" style="width: 911px; height: 575px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730210945720098929.jpg" title="1730210945720098929.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215203.jpg" width="911" height="565" style="width: 911px; height: 565px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">▲与会领导共同启动招聘会</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 本届双选会共327家企业参会，为毕业生提供了上千个招聘岗位，现场气氛热闹非凡。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 毕业生们早早来到双选会现场，主动与企业招聘人员沟通交流，详细询问企业情况、岗位职责和福利待遇等相关信息，并纷纷递上精心准备的个人简历，希望能够在众多求职者中脱颖而出，赢得心仪企业的青睐。同时，现场也有很多在校生前来观摩，提前了解就业形势，做好职业生涯规划。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211006869066181.jpg" title="1730211006869066181.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215240.jpg" width="942" height="534" style="width: 942px; height: 534px;"/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211031863059989.jpg" title="1730211031863059989.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215344.jpg" width="944" height="612" style="width: 944px; height: 612px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211041476062129.jpg" title="1730211041476062129.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215351.jpg" width="946" height="510" style="width: 946px; height: 510px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211079055014725.jpg" title="1730211079055014725.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215313.jpg" width="941" height="522" style="width: 941px; height: 522px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211102817020884.jpg" title="1730211102817020884.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215259.jpg" width="948" height="529" style="width: 948px; height: 529px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211114905006642.jpg" title="1730211114905006642.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215325.jpg" width="944" height="509" style="width: 944px; height: 509px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211138867035417.jpg" title="1730211138867035417.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215339.jpg" width="945" height="416" style="width: 945px; height: 416px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211160692054392.jpg" title="1730211160692054392.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215306.jpg" width="952" height="630" style="width: 952px; height: 630px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211188804050776.jpg" title="1730211188804050776.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215333.jpg" width="957" height="636" style="width: 957px; height: 636px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211216444021102.jpg" title="1730211216444021102.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215357.jpg" width="964" height="644" style="width: 964px; height: 644px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211248248066675.jpg" title="1730211248248066675.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215422.jpg" width="964" height="650" style="width: 964px; height: 650px;"/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 经济管理学院高度重视此次双选会，积极配合学校做好各项相关工作,充分动员我院毕业生参与到双选会中来,鼓励毕业生抓住机会，踊跃展示自己的才华和能力，寻找适合自己的职业发展道路。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211296051055012.jpg" title="1730211296051055012.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215435.jpg" width="960" height="529" style="width: 960px; height: 529px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211312248051830.jpg" title="1730211312248051830.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215414.jpg" width="962" height="551" style="width: 962px; height: 551px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241029/1730211325834057657.jpg" title="1730211325834057657.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241029215403.jpg" width="967" height="577" style="width: 967px; height: 577px;"/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 此次双选会在各方的共同努力下圆满召开，现场人山人海，人头攒动，热闹非凡。双选会为毕业生的就业之路开启了良好的开端。我院深知毕业生就业工作的重要性和紧迫性，在接下来的工作中，会继续全力以赴做好毕业生就业动员工作，助力毕业生顺利实现就业目标，开启人生的新篇章。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><br/></span><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><br/></span><br/></p><p><br style="white-space: normal;"/></p><p><br/></p>